        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900">Our Story</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">
              MakerFriends was founded on a simple belief: that creativity
              flourishes when makers come together to share their knowledge,
              inspire one another, and build lasting friendships.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">
              What started as a small group of enthusiasts tinkering in a garage
              has grown into a global community of over 5,000 makers across 50
              countries, all united by a passion for creating, learning, and
              sharing.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
